	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Writing_Adapted_Screenplay" title="Academy Award for Writing Adapted Screenplay">Best Writing, Screenplay Based on Material from Another Medium</a>.</li>
