	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Actor" title="Academy Award for Best Actor">Best Actor in a Leading Role</a>, (Laurence Harvey)</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Best_Supporting_Actress" title="Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress">Best Actress in a Supporting Role</a> (Hermione Baddeley)</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Academy_Award_for_Directing" title="Academy Award for Directing">Best Director</a> (Jack Clayton)</li>
