      <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Signoret's Oscar win as Best Actress was the first time that a <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_cinema" title="French cinema">French cinema</a> actress had won that award.</p>
